



My Lord,
New York april 23d 1776.



Understanding that the Committee of Safety, for this Colony, have given your Lordship permission to visit Bermuda for the benefit of your health, I take the liberty of wishing you a pleasant Voyage, and a speedy and perfect restoration of it1with respect, I have the honour to be Yr Lordships Most Obedt, & Most Hble Servt

Go: Washington

